outline:

  • Programming Concept & Theory
  • Loop
  • Conditional Statement

  • Array & Object
  • Coding Challenge

title: Laravel 9
description: Laravel 9 courses will teach you to understand not only theory but also real world concept . In this course, You can learn basic theory and real world useful PHP's packages in laravel. Finally You can practice with News Projects.
outline:
1. Laravel Introduction & Installation
2. Routing
3. Controller
4. View
5.Blade Template and Layouts
6. str() helper function
7.Http Session
8. Form Request
9. Validation
10. Middleware
11. Starting With Database
12. Migrations
13. Seeding
14. Query Builder (CRUD)
15. Eloquent Model (CRUD with File)
16. Relationship (One to One, One to Many, Many to Many)
17. Ajax CRUD
19. Custom 404 pages and Sweet alert
20. Collection
21. Jetstream Auth
22. Multiple Roles Using Jetstream
23. Mail SMTP (Contact Form)
24. Excel (Export/Import)
25. Api Using Sanctum Auth
